#2.What is the difference between implicit and explicit type conversion? Give one example of each.

->implicit conversion- It converts automatically smaller data types into larger ones to prevent
         data loss.
         ex- x=4
             y=6.5
             z=x+y //convert int into float
             print(z)//output->10.5

   explicit conversion- It convert data type manually using built in function 
                     like int(),float(),bool(),str()
            ex- x="20"
                y=int(x) // convert str int int
                print(y+2)//output-> 22




